                  </persName>
            ,</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17840915-8-verdict41" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17840915-8-verdict41" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               NOT GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the London Jury before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
            </div1>
